OL,3,CBritain facing 'urgent crisis', major
OL,4,Creview into workplace sickness warns
OL,6,FThe UK is "sliding into an avoidable
OL,7,Fcrisis", the author of a major review
OL,8,Fon how to keep people in work has
OL,9,Fwarned, as he urged a reduced reliance
OL,10,Fon 'fit notes' amid an "enormous" cost
OL,11,Fto employers from ill health among
OL,12,Fworkers.
OL,14,FFormer John Lewis boss Sir Charlie
OL,15,FMayfield's report found that poor
OL,16,Fworkplace health costs UK employers
OL,17,Faround #85 billion a year.
OL,19,FIt also warned that Britons being
OL,20,Funable to work due to ill health is
OL,21,Fcosting the country around 7% of GDP.
