OL,3,CBritain facing 'urgent crisis', major
OL,4,Creview into workplace sickness warns
OL,6,FMayfield said there is "broad
OL,7,Frecognition that Britain is facing a
OL,8,Fquiet but urgent crisis," with ill
OL,9,Fhealth now one of the biggest drivers
OL,10,Fof economic inactivity in the UK.
OL,12,FHis review, published on Wednesday,
OL,13,Ftold of a culture of fear among
OL,14,Fworkers around ill health, a lack of
OL,15,Fan effective or consistent support
OL,16,Fsystem for employers and employees in
OL,17,Fmanaging health, and structural
OL,18,Fchallenges for disabled people.
