OL,3,CBritain facing 'urgent crisis', major
OL,4,Creview into workplace sickness warns
OL,6,FMayfield said that while supportive
OL,7,Fworkplaces matter, "so does personal
OL,8,Fresponsibility," as he warned that
OL,9,Fdisengaging from work and potential
OL,10,Fsupport "leads to detachment and
OL,11,Fdependency."
OL,13,FHe described 'fit notes', sometimes
OL,14,Fknown as sick notes, as "often
OL,15,Fproblematic," becoming a "barrier to
OL,16,Fcontact, further embedding distance
OL,17,Fbetween employer and employee".
