OL,3,CBritain facing 'urgent crisis', major
OL,4,Creview into workplace sickness warns
OL,6,FHe reiterated that 93% of fit notes in
OL,7,FEngland deem the patient "not fit for
OL,8,Fwork" and are "often" extended without
OL,9,Ffurther consultation.
OL,11,FThe government has long argued too
OL,12,Fmany people are being written off and
OL,13,Fout of work.
OL,15,FThere are 800,000 more people out of
OL,16,Fwork now than in 2019 due to health
OL,17,Fproblems and, the review states,
OL,18,F"without decisive action to address
OL,19,Fthis trend, projections show we are on
OL,20,Ftrack to add another 600,000 by 2030".
