OL,3,CBritain facing 'urgent crisis', major
OL,4,Creview into workplace sickness warns
OL,6,FIt adds that the increase in 16 to 34-
OL,7,Fyear-olds with a mental health
OL,8,Fcondition who are economically
OL,9,Finactive due to long-term sickness is
OL,10,F"particularly concerning," rising by
OL,11,F190,000 (76%) between 2019 and 2024.
OL,13,FBarriers to work for disabled people
OL,14,Fare "particularly stark", the review
OL,15,Fsaid, with only 53% of this group in
OL,16,Fwork.
