OL,3,CBritain facing 'urgent crisis', major
OL,4,Creview into workplace sickness warns
OL,6,FMayfield said: "Britain is sliding
OL,7,Finto an avoidable crisis. Ill health
OL,8,Fhas become one of the biggest brakes
OL,9,Fon growth and opportunity. But this is
OL,10,Fnot inevitable."
OL,12,FAmong its recommendations, the review
OL,13,Fcalled for the adoption of a workplace
OL,14,Fhealth provision, supporting employees
OL,15,Fand line managers across a so-called
OL,16,Fhealthy working lifecycle.
