OL,6,FIt said this approach, offering
OL,7,Fsupport and advice and early
OL,8,Fintervention, could be integrated with
OL,9,Fthe NHS App and reduce or replace the
OL,10,Fneed for the current fit note.
OL,12,FThe government said more than 60
OL,13,Femployers ` including the British Beer
OL,14,Fand Pub Association, Burger King, John
OL,15,FLewis and Google UK ` have expressed
OL,16,Finterest in becoming so-called
OL,17,Fvanguard employers to pioneer the
OL,18,Foverall new approach.
