OL,6,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,7,FMcFadden said Mayfield's message is
OL,8,F"crystal clear: keeping people healthy
OL,9,Fand in work is the right thing to do
OL,10,Fand is essential for economic growth".
OL,12,FHe added: "Business is our partner in
OL,13,Fbuilding a productive workforce `
OL,14,Fbecause when businesses retain talent
OL,15,Fand reduce workplace ill health,
OL,16,Feveryone wins.
