OL,6,FIn a similar tone, Reform UK announced
OL,7,Flast week their intention to cut
OL,8,Funemployment benefits from those with
OL,9,F"non-serious anxiety disorders", with
OL,10,FReform MP Lee Anderson claiming
OL,11,Freturning to work was the best
OL,12,Ftreatment for them.
OL,14,FThe chancellor was herself asked about
OL,15,Fthis on Tuesday, and whilst she
OL,16,Fconceded people with anxiety are "much
OL,17,Fbetter served if they are given the
OL,18,Fsupport to get back into work", she
OL,19,Fsaid ultimately it was a decision for
OL,20,Fhealthcare practitioners.
